The '''2007 [[Qatar ExxonMobil Open|Qatar Open]]''', known as the '''2007 Qatar [[ExxonMobil]] Open''', for sponsorship reasons, was  men's [[2007 ATP Tour|ATP Tour]] [[tennis]] tournament held in [[Doha, Qatar]] from 1 January until 6 January 2007.

The tournament saw [[Ivan Ljubičić]] claim his first of two tournaments this year, and also saw him temporarily lead the ATP race.

==Champions==
===Singles===
{{main|2007 Qatar Open – Singles}}
{{flagicon|CRO}} '''[[Ivan Ljubičić]]''' defeated {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Andy Murray]], 6–4, 6–4

===Doubles===
{{main|2007 Qatar Open – Doubles}}
{{flagicon|RUS}} '''[[Mikhail Youzhny]]''' / {{flagicon|SRB}} '''[[Nenad Zimonjić]]''' defeated {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Martin Damm]] / {{flagicon|IND}} [[Leander Paes]], 6–1, 7–6<sup>(7–3)</sup>

