{{coord|55|44|21|N|24|21|34|E|type:landmark|display=title}} {{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Aukštaitijos stadionas | image = [[File:Aukstaitijos stadionas Is Panevezio boksto.JPG|250px]] '''[[UEFA stadium categories|UEFA Category 2 stadium]]''' | location = [[Panevėžys]], [[Lithuania]] | opened = 1965 | renovated = 2008 | surface = Grass | seating_capacity = 4,000 seated | tenants = [[FK Panevėžys]]| }}
'''Aukštaitija Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Panevėžys]], [[Lithuania]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[FK Panevėžys]] and earlier of [[FK Ekranas| FK Ekranas Panevėžys]]. It is named [[Aukštaitija]], one of the five [[regions of Lithuania]].
==See also== *[http://www.fkekranas.lt/klubas/aukstaitijos-stadionas Official FK Ekranas Website In English] *[http://www.futbolas.lt Official Lithuanian Football Federation Website]
