Most recently, Bermuda took part in the [[2009 ICC Americas Under-19 Championship]], finishing 3rd and so just missing out on the chance to progress to the [[2009 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup Qualifier|World Cup Qualifier]]. They won three matches losing only to [[Canada Under-19 cricket team|Canada]] and [[United States Under-19 cricket team|the United States]].<ref name=2009champ>[http://www.cricketeurope4.net/CRICKETEUROPE/DATABASE/2009/TOURNAMENTS/AMERICASU19/about.shtml Americas Under 19 Championship 2009] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203142900/http://www.cricketeurope4.net/CRICKETEUROPE/DATABASE/2009/TOURNAMENTS/AMERICASU19/about.shtml |date=3 February 2010 }} cricketeurope4.net 10/12/10</ref>
