{{Use Australian English|date=January 2018}}
[[File:Footytips screenshot.jpg|thumb|right|280px|A [[screenshot]] of a team in the Footytips competition.]]
'''Fantasy football''' is a [[fantasy sport]] in which competitors score points based on the performance of players in the [[Australian Football League]]. The two biggest competitions are the [[Herald Sun]]'s [[AFL SuperCoach|Supercoach]] competition and the [[Australian Football League|AFL]]'s [[AFL Dream Team|Dream Team]] competition.<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theaustralian.com.au/media/clash-over-fantasy-football/story-e6frg996-1225697028039| title = Rivals scramble for fantasy football dollars | first =Simon | last =Canning |work =[[The Australian]]| date =13 April 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.abc.net.au/mediawatch/transcripts/s3472295.htm| title = Paying for news}}</ref> Both games are designed and run by [[Vapormedia]].<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.smh.com.au/afl/afl-news/finding-the-magical-bargain-the-cult-of-fantasy-footy-20110323-1c6jl.html | title =Finding the magical bargain: the cult of fantasy footy|date=23 March 2011| first =Will| last = Brodie| work=The Sydney Morning Herald}}</ref>

Other competitions include [[Fox Sports (Australia)|Fox Sport]]'s Fantasy AFL,<ref>[http://aflfantasy.foxsports.com.au/M/home.mc Fantasy AFL]</ref> [[Yahoo!7]]'s AFL Football Fantasy,<ref>[http://afl.yahoo.virtualsports.com.au/?p=index AFL Football Fantasy]</ref> Footytips,<ref>[http://www.footytips.com.au/cfm/ft/engine/engine.cfm?l1=Fantasy&l2=Fantasy.MyTeams&ref=navh Fantasy AFL]</ref> Ultimate Footy<ref>[http://www.ultimatefooty.com/ Ultimate Footy - Draft Style Fantasy AFL]</ref> and FantasyFooty.net.au <ref>[http://www.fantasyfooty.net.au/ FantasyFooty.net.au - Draft Style Fantasy AFL]</ref> (formally My Fantasy Footy).

