The '''Federação Sergipana de Futebol''' ([[English language|English]]: Football Association of Sergipe state) was founded on November 10, 1926, and it manages all the official [[association football|football]] tournaments within the state of [[Sergipe]], which are the [[Campeonato Sergipano]], the [[Campeonato Sergipano (lower levels)|Campeonato Sergipano Série A2]] and the [[Copa Governador do Estado de Sergipe]], and represents the clubs at the [[Brazilian Football Confederation|Brazilian Football Confederation (CBF)]].

