'''Krohnsminde kunstgressbane''' is a municipality-owned [[sports ground]] and football [[stadium]] located in the city of [[Bergen]], [[Norway]], near [[Danmarks plass]] in the borough of [[Årstad, Bergen|Årstad]]. It was the home of the football club [[Løv-Ham Fotball|Løv-Ham]] until 2008. The western [[Terrace (stadium)|terrace]] of Krohnsminde kunstgressbane was demolished in November/December 2008 to make room for a new hospital building.<ref name='ba1'>{{cite news | first=Øystein | last=Riise | coauthors= |authorlink= | title=River tribune for å bygge sykehus | date=August 8, 2008 | publisher= | url =http://www.ba.no/nyheter/article3710589.ece | work =[[Bergensavisen]] | pages = | accessdate = 2008-12-16 | language = Norwegian }}</ref>

The terrace was designed by the architect [[Ole Landmark]] and finished in 1947.<ref name='bt1'>{{cite news | first=Pål Andreas | last=Mæland | coauthors= |authorlink= | title=Drømmen om Danmarks plass | date=August 25, 2008 | publisher= | url =http://www.bt.no/lokalt/bergen/article617603.ece | work =[[Bergens Tidende]] | pages = | accessdate = 2008-12-16 | language = Norwegian }}</ref> The venue has hosted the Norwegian Athletics Championships in 1950, 1957 and 1961.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.friidrett.no/stevner/statistikk/nm/Documents/amnm.htm |title=Main Championships Men |publisher=[[Norwegian Athletics Association]] |language=Norwegian |accessdate=25 November 2011 |archivedate=25 November 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/63SxANU6u?url=http://www.friidrett.no/stevner/statistikk/nm/Documents/amnm.htm |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref> In the [[1991 Norwegian Premier League|1991 season]], it hosted the 11 home matches for [[Fyllingen Fotball|Fyllingen]] in the [[Norwegian Premier League]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Foran seriestart Fyllingen på ny kurs |work=[[Aftenposten]] |last=Dehlin |first=Håkon |date=18 April 1991 |page=35 |language=Norwegian}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Norsk fotball-leksikon |last=Fagerli |first=Arnfinn |last2=Nilsen |first2=Christian Lunde |publisher=Orion |year=1999 |isbn=82-458-0398-7 |language=Norwegian |page=387}}</ref>

