{{Infobox football club |clubname = Soyombiin Barsuud FC |image = Soyombyn_Barsuud_FC_Logo.png |fullname = Soyombii Barsuud Football Club |founded = 2009 |ground = ''None Stadium'' |capacity = ''None'' | pattern_la1 = _fcbarcelona1516a | pattern_b1 = _fcbarcelona1516away | pattern_ra1 = _fcbarcelona1516a | pattern_sh1 = _yellow | pattern_so1 = _yellow | leftarm1 = FCCD00 | body1 = FCCD01 | rightarm1 = FCCD00 | shorts1 = FCCD00 | socks1 = FCCD00 | pattern_la2=_england14a|pattern_b2=_england14a|pattern_ra2=_england14a|pattern_sh2=_red_stripes|pattern_so2= | leftarm2=FF0000|body2=FF0000|rightarm2=FF0000|shorts2=FF0000|socks2=FF0000 }}
'''Soyombiin Barsuud''' is a [[Association football|football]] club from [[Ulaanbaatar]], [[Mongolia]]. They currently play in the [[Mongolia National Premier League]], the highest level of football in Mongolia, making their debut appearance in the [[2015 Mongolia Premier League|2015 season]].<ref name="RSSSF">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesm/mong2015.html|title=Mongolia 2014|last1=Stokkermans|first1=Karel|website=www.rsssf.com|publisher=RSSSF|accessdate=22 August 2014}}</ref> They have no professional footballers.
