The '''Ulriksdal dirt course''' was a course located 6&nbsp;km north of [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]] at [[Ulriksdal Palace|Ulriksdal]]. It hosted part of the cross-country portion of the eventing competition for the [[Equestrian at the 1956 Summer Olympics|equestrian]] events at the [[1956 Summer Olympics]].

